Ruby-on-Rails</a>
which is an important part of the software stack used by OpenProject
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20469">#20469</a>).</p>

<p>For further information on the release, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/732">Changelog
